        "action": "Limit prorogation of parliament to 4 days to stop misuse of prerogative powers",
        "additional_details": "This can be used to \u2018bypass\u2019 parliament in certain circumstances and there is no reasonable or practical reason why prorogation should take longer than 4 days.",
